Default theme implementation to display a Bootstrap Input+Button component.

@var id:          Your id
@var name:        Your name
@var class:       Your class
@var value:       Your content

How to use it:
    {% include "@Core/components/span.html.twig" with {id:'spanId', name:'spanName', class: '', value: ''} %}
